thread.title: BRIEF-Telecity says EC review of merger with Equinix extended
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Telecity says EC review of merger with Equinix extended | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Telecity says EC review of merger with Equinix extended
text:
Oct 23 Telecity Group Plc
* Update on recommended transaction with equinix
* Confirms ec has entered into a period of market testing based upon commitments proposed by equinix and telecitygroup
* As a result, european commission's phase i review timetable is extended to 13 november 2015 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reporting By London Bureau)
